  <p align="left">With the Winter-season now upon us, we would like to treat you to a hot chocolate or cup of coffee, as you sit down, relax and read the following.</p>
  <p>  <strong>THE GATHERING</strong><br>
  The countdown is on for this year&rsquo;s Gathering, during 15-19 July in Palmerston North: <a href="http://www.highlandhome.co.nz">www.highlandhome.co.nz</a></p>
  <p>Soon you will be receiving information to help you prepare. As we did last year, we will be inviting some of the people who journey alongside us, to the Gathering. Do you know someone that needs to be there? The Gathering is a time for members, families &amp; volunteers/friends connected with Incedo to get together. We have an invitation letter if you&rsquo;d like a copy to send to someone.</p>
  <p>The cost of the Gathering is $140pp. (Special Family rate is $280.) Let someone from the MLT know if you have concerns about your travel and Gathering costs, but please let us know this by the 1st July.</p>
  <p>We would like regional team members to co-ordinate some activities during the Gathering. Your team activity should reflect: at least 2 Incedo values, be interactive and relevant for members, invited volunteers/friends and Incedo families - approx 35 adults and 15 children.<br>
      <br>
      Activity time length: approximately 30 minutes. Aim to meet as a team before 1st July to discuss and plan together. Writing pens, felt pens and a roll of newsprint will be available. Any other props: please bring with you.<br>
      <br>
      Regional teams:</p>
